"including backups, is encrypted at rest using industry-standard AES-256 "
"encryption (via AWS KMS). This ensures that even in the highly unlikely "
"event of physical hardware compromise, your data remains irretrievable "
"without the necessary decryption keys."
msgstr ""

#: templates/security.html:58
