msgstr ""

#: templates/security.html:63
msgid ""
"Every interaction you have with TrackMyRupee is secured. We enforce strict "
"HTTPS connections for all traffic between your browser or device and our "
"servers. Additionally, all connections between our application servers and "
"our Supabase database are securely encrypted using TLS (Transport Layer "
"Security), preventing any interception, tampering, or eavesdropping of your "
"sensitive financial information as it travels across the internet."
msgstr ""

#: templates/security.html:82
msgid "Automated Backups"
msgstr ""

#: templates/security.html:87
msgid ""
"Your data's availability and durability are critical. We leverage Supabase's"
" automated database backup systems to securely back up our database "
"architecture daily. These backups are stored in geographically redundant "
"locations and enable data recovery in the highly unlikely event of data "
"corruption or a catastrophic system failure."
msgstr ""

#: templates/security.html:111
